longDescription: Slip on your bell bottoms and light a lava lamp!  It’s the Super ‘70s with DJs who boogie down and spin 45 rpm records.  Polyester outfits, pet rocks, CB radios and disco from a galaxy far, far away!  Far out, man!
mediumDescription: Pop tunes and pop DJs from the wild and funky decade of mood rings, disco and bell bottoms!  The Super 70s!
